text: Hugo Licher (10 March 1902 - 14 April 1943) was a Dutch gymnast. He competed in seven events at the 1928 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1902 births Category:1943 deaths Category:Dutch male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of the Netherlands Category:Gymnasts at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Duisburg
